{"tid":2388777,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"巴西居酒屋被揭大搞「多人運動」雜交派對","createTime":"2021-01-31T11:23:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-31T14:08:04.000Z","uid":66271,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a023b3b964e590dbd987f9d29ec10df2144dd42c","tid":2388777,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T11:23:14.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎疫情在全球持續延燒，各國政府也紛紛呼籲民眾做好防疫措施，保護自己與他人。不過位在巴西的一間日式居酒屋，近日被爆出業者大喇喇的舉辦「雜交派對」，多人混戰畫面曝光後，讓不少網友痛批太誇張。現在業者已發布道歉聲明，直呼自己知道錯了，將對店裏進行消毒，未來也絕不再犯。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，這間居酒屋「Izakaya Hyotan」位在巴西庫里蒂巴市（curitiba），在去年3月曾為了防疫「自主停業」，還被不少民眾評比為「優良餐廳」，想不到過了不到一年的時間，竟被爆出業者不顧防疫舉辦雜交趴。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210129/431819030618312704064913.jpeg/iDDMZLZ7DRcKw6cAVDac_FZSaFCuc3FMNepdFjXqXRY?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210129%2F431819030618312704064913.jpeg%2FiDDMZLZ7DRcKw6cAVDac_FZSaFCuc3FMNepdFjXqXRY%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=bcf98187&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210129/431819032719790080716043.jpeg/C5RQeA_VvY5O6juSubeybCJk4XNz4IldflOkxH5TpMQ?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210129%2F431819032719790080716043.jpeg%2FC5RQeA_VvY5O6juSubeybCJk4XNz4IldflOkxH5TpMQ%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=765d10b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210129/431819037379923968857302.jpeg/uMHNwtCMv7_yOvs_O_xBxGfOhx_YojIA4uBOteLgTrU?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210129%2F431819037379923968857302.jpeg%2FuMHNwtCMv7_yOvs_O_xBxGfOhx_YojIA4uBOteLgTrU%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=30a65cdd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據報導，這場多人派對在本月23日餐廳打烊後舉辦，參加者都是員工，他們不只在廚房、客用餐桌上進行性行為、還上演「多人運動」，連SM也是活動環節之一。<br />\n<br />\n消息曝光後，讓網友痛批「太誇張」，連當地政府也特別關切，目前正進行相關調查。而居酒屋業者27日也在Instagram上發布道歉聲明，以日本「土下座」漫畫搭配長文，直呼自己真的知道錯了，請大家相信他不是壞人，店裏會進行消毒，以後絕對不會再犯。"},{"pid":"989489947dbbe762b37dad3bbcd71e90ec89e858","tid":2388777,"uid":70786,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T11:29:25.000Z","msg":"體液清酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6617a2ccc1bb02bca5b24974424a89fcbf243f0f","tid":2388777,"uid":30868,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T11:37:05.000Z","msg":"想做員工了"},{"pid":"a3471b428398dd4a2678f48571caab31ebe723a5","tid":2388777,"uid":131278,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T11:38:51.000Z","msg":"比噁心程度<br />\n正評：巴西精蛋<br />\nVS<br />\n負皮：二見師傅茶碗蒸"},{"pid":"ad18cac60918d3b66ea9a264438601819d509fd2","tid":2388777,"uid":44209,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T11:40:21.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">習</span></span></strong>交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ef6c552fd5e38cbc54f6a2d39b52fcd1f698864","tid":2388777,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T12:36:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想join"},{"pid":"494dacf77f94224d0a5a48884820466b9c51a8ac","tid":2388777,"uid":212246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T13:50:14.000Z","msg":"人體盛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e2a4b78618a99bd772dc459f094ff47ef94a027","tid":2388777,"uid":114097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T14:02:30.000Z","msg":"我入到嚟"},{"pid":"e082a58a71b526471d9a61c8dbc0fcb24887d3ef","tid":2388777,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T14:08:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"h